      <title>富裕的加勒比海岛国正试图撼动全球援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/rich-islands-eschew-vulgar-gdp-in-plan-to-shake-up-global-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些富裕的加勒比国家正试图重组全球金融体系，以减少对中国的依赖并增加融资渠道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/rich-islands-eschew-vulgar-gdp-in-plan-to-shake-up-global-aid</guid>
