    <item>
      <title>法国左翼联盟在选举民意调查中与勒庞差距进一步拉大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/french-leftist-alliance-edges-closer-to-le-pen-in-election-poll</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据周一公布的投票意向民意调查显示，玛丽娜·勒庞领导的极右翼国民联盟将在法国立法选举首轮中获得 33% 的支持率，而左翼政党联盟将获得 28% 的支持率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/french-leftist-alliance-edges-closer-to-le-pen-in-election-poll</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 15:16:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油资源丰富的安哥拉银行面临较高的洗钱风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/oil-rich-angola-sees-high-risk-of-money-laundering-for-its-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[安哥拉正试图避免被列入全球非法金融监视名单，并表示这个产油国的银行业存在“高洗钱风险”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/oil-rich-angola-sees-high-risk-of-money-laundering-for-its-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 15:14:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国政府问责署称，美国陆军新型高超音速武器仍需数月时间才能问世</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/us-army-s-new-hypersonic-weapon-is-still-months-away-gao-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国会审计发现，美国军方不太可能在 10 月 1 日开始的财政年度之前交付足够数量的首批高超音速武器以供作战，这进一步推迟了中国和俄罗斯已经部署的下一代导弹的部署。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/us-army-s-new-hypersonic-weapon-is-still-months-away-gao-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 14:57:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国游说团体呼吁选举前承担预算责任</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/french-lobby-calls-for-budgetary-responsibility-before-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国商业游说团体表示，即将举行的提前立法选举对该国的经济未来至关重要，并呼吁保持开放和稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/french-lobby-calls-for-budgetary-responsibility-before-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 14:48:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
